displayProperties.description: Complete a run of each Year 6 raid and dungeon to earn the 2023 raid patch.

displayProperties.name: Sundering
displayProperties.description:
Destroying vehicles and constructs grants this weapon bonus reload speed and charge rate.

Constructs include barricades, turrets, Stasis crystals, and other objects created in the field.

displayProperties.name: Deconstruct
displayProperties.description:
Dealing sustained damage grants bonus damage against vehicles and constructs for an improved duration and partially refills the magazine from reserves. Damage with Primary ammo or against constructs provides additional progress.

Constructs include barricades, turrets, Stasis crystals, and other objects created in the field.

displayProperties.name: Dawning Memento
displayProperties.description:
A rare curio obtained from The Dawning.

When inserted into a Shaped weapon at the Relic on Mars, this Memento will grant the weapon additional vanity options.

You may only store one of these Mementos at a time.

displayProperties.name: In the Shadow of the Mountain
displayProperties.description:
Find and restore three lost Bones of Hefnd:
- First Bone: Across the bridge inside the first fort, before an arresting Knight assails you.
- Second Bone: Across from imprisonment, after ascending through the ceiling.
- Third Bone: At the top of the summit, face back from the cliff and find shelter.

setData.questLineName: In the Shadow of the Mountain

displayProperties.name: A Parting Gift
displayProperties.description: An incantation to unveil the deepest mysteries of the Imbaru Engine.

displayProperties.name: In the Shadow of the Mountain
displayProperties.description: Return to Ikora and report your findings.

displayProperties.name: Buried Bloodline Catalyst
displayProperties.description:
Upgrades this weapon to a Masterwork. Once upgraded, the weapon will obtain enhanced capabilities, such as increased stats and/or additional perks.

Defeat targets using this weapon to unlock this upgrade.

displayProperties.name: Dawning Memento
displayProperties.description:
A rare curio obtained from The Dawning.

When inserted into a Shaped weapon at the Relic on Mars, this Memento will grant the weapon additional vanity options.

You may only store one of these Mementos at a time.

displayProperties.name: In the Shadow of the Mountain
displayProperties.description:
Find and restore the three final lost Bones of Hefnd:
- Seventh Bone: Within the maze, stride spanning a pitfall, light calls through the window.
- Eighth Bone: The Taken roil at cave's bottom sends you to scurry over boulders into a ruined alcove.
- Ninth Bone: Within a tunnel on the broken cliffs, brave the Taken storm.

displayProperties.name: In the Shadow of the Mountain
displayProperties.description:
Find and restore three more lost Bones of Hefnd:
- Fourth Bone: In the snowfallen maze, through the broken wall, seek the banner of kings.
- Fifth Bone: Cross into the Tempest, through the portcullis, at the sewer's mouth.
- Sixth Bone: At summit's base, find shelter off the beaten path. Too far, and the Taken will descend upon you.

displayProperties.name: Upgrade Ghost
displayProperties.description: Upgrade this Ghost to increase its energy capacity by 1. Fully upgrading this Ghost to Masterwork provides an additional mod socket.

displayProperties.name: Hungering Quarrel
displayProperties.description: Double fires tracking bolts. Landing bolts leeches health from the target.

displayProperties.name: Activity Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: Activity mods provide additional currency and material rewards in various activities.

displayProperties.name: Violent Reanimation
displayProperties.description: Multiple final blows with this weapon grant Devour to the wielder.

displayProperties.name: Tracking Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: Tracking mods increase the range of the detection of caches and resources out in the field.

displayProperties.name: Kill Tracker
displayProperties.description: This weapon tracks the number of enemies you defeated with it.

displayProperties.name: Hard Launch
displayProperties.description:
This weapon's launch barrel is optimized for projectile speed.
  •  Greatly increases projectile speed
  •  Decreases stability
  •  Slightly decreases blast radius

displayProperties.name: Hand-Laid Stock
displayProperties.description:
This weapon is optimized for recoil control.
  •  Increases stability

displayProperties.name: Empty Catalyst Socket
displayProperties.description:
An Exotic catalyst can be inserted into this socket.

Check the Exotic catalysts section in Triumphs to learn where the catalyst can be obtained.

displayProperties.name: Economic Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: Economic mods increase currency and resource gains from sources.

displayProperties.name: No Projection
displayProperties.description: Restores your Ghost to an empty projection.

displayProperties.name: Flared Magwell
displayProperties.description:
Optimized for fast reloading.
  •  Slightly increases stability
  •  Greatly increases reload speed

displayProperties.name: Activity Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: Available once the Ghost shell has been fully Masterworked.

displayProperties.name: Experience Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: Experience mods increase global experience gains.

displayProperties.name: Default Shader
displayProperties.description: Restores your gear to its default colors.
